title: Sound On: Musk Bails on Twitter Deal, June Jobs Data
itunes:title: Sound On: Musk Bails on Twitter Deal, June Jobs Data
description:
Today's guests: Austan Goolsbee, Professor of Economics at Booth School of Economy at University of Chicago discusses June's jobs report and Bloomberg Politics Contributors Jeanne Sheehan Zaino and Rick Davis discuss Elon Musk's decision to terminate his bid to buy Twitter. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
